name: Jungle Passthrough Demo
summary:
Demo of Jungle Passthrough
create a jungle in your home with a sample of the plants and animals from the full game "Jungle Passthrough" that can be moved to create your own customer jungle, some plants on full random spawn in demo
optional handtracking
bonus passthrough samples to interact with from other games in the lobby

Compare to the full game with 70+ Plants and jungle objects, 60+ Animals, 5+ bonus pieces of furniture with various premade levels and spawnable...
